import math

def minimum_headings_needed(s1: str, s2: str) -> int:
    na = len(s1)
    nb = len(s2)
    dp = [[-1 for _ in range(26)] for _ in range(na + 1)]
    for i in range(na - 1, -1, -1):
        for j in range(26):
            dp[i][j] = dp[i + 1][j]
        dp[i][ord(s1[i]) - 97] = i
    cp = 1
    ans = 1
    i = 0
    while i < nb:
        if cp == na:
            ans += 1
            cp = 0
        if dp[cp][ord(s2[i]) - 97] == -1:
            ans += 1
            cp = 0
            if dp[cp][ord(s2[i]) - 97] == -1:
                ans = math.inf
                break
        cp = dp[cp][ord(s2[i]) - 97] + 1
        i += 1
    return ans if ans != math.inf else -1
